{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九章\"红颜祸水\"中，楚留香目睹天鹰子被杀灭口后，追查线索至济南。他在街上偶遇天星帮的沈珊姑，跟踪她来到城中贫民窟，寻找一位名叫孙学圃的老画师。沈珊姑手持一幅美人画像追问孙学圃画中人身份，孙学圃起初推诿，最终承认自己正是二十年前为画中女子画像的画师——他因画成后被她灌醉并挖去双眼，从此沦落为算命瞎子。在威逼之下，孙学圃道出那女子的名字——秋灵素。楚留香惊觉此名与天鹰子包袱中的短笺\"灵素\"吻合，原来秋灵素与左又铮、西门千、灵鹫子三人皆有情感纠葛，这三位男子皆因她而终身不娶或出家，如今三人均已横死。楚留香现身与沈珊姑相见，两人均欲寻找这神秘的秋灵素。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽未杀你，但你却因我而死，只因那人若非知道我要来寻你，也就未必会杀你，只可惜你生前虽然掌握着那秘密的关键，你自己却不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "半大孩子",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "妈，她说孙秀才，就是孙老头呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "哦！你要找孙老头，他就住在上面第七间屋子里，门口挂着八卦门帘的就是，好找得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你就是孙学圃孙秀才？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "是，我就是孙学圃，问卦两分银子，批命一钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我找的是画师孙秀才，不是算命的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我就是画师孙秀才，只不过二十年前就改行了，姑娘若要画像，只怕已来迟了二十年。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你改行不改行都没关系，只要你真是二十年前专替人画像的孙学圃，我找的就是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我问你，这幅画是不是你画的？画上的人是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我不知道这幅画是谁画的，也不知道画上的人是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你怎会不知道？这画上明明有你的题名。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "放开你的手，你难道也和我一样，竟看不出我是个瞎子？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你……你什么都瞧不见了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我眼睛若还有一线光明，又怎会放下我的画笔，绘画就是我的生命，我早已失去生命，现在坐在这里的，只不过是一具活的死尸而已。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你虽已瞧不见画上的人，但你也应记得她的，她是一个美人，你可记得你曾经画过美人？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "现在，我虽然是个又穷又老的瞎子，但二十年前，……二十年前我孙学圃却是个鼎鼎大名的人物。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "二十年前，人们将我比之为曹不兴，比之为吴道子，普天之下，哪一位名门闺秀不想求我为她画像，我画过的美人也不知多少。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "但这一个却不同……你一定得相信我，无论你画过的美人有多少，你必定不会忘记她的，无论谁只要瞧过她的脸，都再也不会忘记。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "你说的这幅画，可是宽两尺，长三尺，画上的人可是穿着件青色的衣服，镶着蓝边，脚下伏着只黑色狸猫……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "不错，就是这幅画，我知道你必定记得的，你当然也必定会记得画上的美人是谁？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "你问的竟是她……你问的竟是她……我……我不记得她是谁，我根本不认识她……我根本没有见过她。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你是见过她的，是么？你也记得她，是么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "姑娘，求求你，放过我吧，我……我只是个又穷又瞎的无用老头子，在这里安静地等死，你何苦还要来逼我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你不说，我就宰了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "好，我说，她……她不是个人，是个魔女。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "魔女？如此美丽的女子，怎会是魔女？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "不错，她的确是美丽的，我一生中见过的美女虽多，但却再也没有一个人能及得上她，别人的美丽最多使你眼花，但她的美丽却可使你发疯，使你宁可牺牲一切，甚至不惜牺牲生命，只为求得她对你一笑。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我见着她时，也不禁被她的美丽惊倒，当时我并不像现在这般老丑，而且还可说是个翩翩美男子，也曾经有不少女子，为我相思，我都不曾一顾，但是她……在她面前，我竟似突然变成了她的奴隶，恨不得将我所有的一切全都拿出来，全都奉献到她的脚下。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "世上真有这么美丽的女子么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "没有见过她的人，委实难以相信，这幅画，我自信还画得不错，但却又怎能画出她那醉人的神采、谈吐……我简直画不出她美丽的万一。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "她找你，就是为了要画像？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "不错，她见了我后，就要我为她画四幅像，我费了三个月的功夫，用尽我一切智慧、心血，终于完成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "这三个月里，我天天面对着她……这三个月真是我毕生最幸福的时刻，但三个月后，她……她……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "三个月后怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "三……三个月后，我将四幅画完成的那天晚上，她备下一桌精致的酒席，亲自来为我倒酒，陪我共饮，我神魂颠倒，不觉醉了，等我醒来，才知道她……她竟将我一双眼睛生生挖了去。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "她为什么要这样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "只因我为她画过像后，她再也不愿我为别的女人画像了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔女……这果然是个魔女。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我早已说过，她是个魔女，无论谁占有她，都只有不幸，姑娘你……你为何要问她？这幅画又怎会落到你手里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "这幅画乃是我大师兄左又铮的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "既是如此，她的来历，你为何不去问你的师兄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我大师兄已失踪了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "失踪……失踪以前呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "以前我自然也问过，但他却是不肯说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "他既然不肯说，你为何定要问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我大师兄终身不娶，就是为了这女子，我大师兄一生的幸福，可说都是葬送在这女子的手里，为她朝思暮想，神魂颠倒，数十年从未改变，但她却显然对我大师兄漠不关心，她给我大师兄的，惟有痛苦而已。",
      "tone": "恨声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "你要找她，就是为了要替你师兄报复？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "不错，我恨她……恨她。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "你恨她，可是为了你很喜欢你的大师兄？若不是她，也许你早已成了你大师兄的妻子，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我恨她，还有一个别的原因。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "我大师兄这次出门的前一天晚上，曾经接着一封书信，然后就坐在这画像前，痴痴的坐了一夜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "然后他出门后就没有回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "不错，所以，我想我大师兄的失踪，必定和她有关系，那封信说不定就是她搞的鬼，若能找到她，说不定就能找到大师兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我只知道她的名字叫秋灵素。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "姑娘千万莫要吃惊，在下此来，也正和姑娘的目的一样，也是来寻访这位秋夫人秋灵素的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为何要找她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认得她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "我不认得她，幸好不认得她。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你们是谁，你们都是来打听她的下落的，现在，我已告诉了你们，你们也可以走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "她现在在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "speaker_name": "孙学圃",
      "listener": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "text": "自从那天晚上之后，我就没有再见过她……或许我应该说，自从那天晚上后，我就没有再听过她的声音。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_shan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "沈珊姑",
      "listener": "char_sun_xue_pu",
      "text": "你只是告诉我她的名字，那又有什么用？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    }
